data.text:
Here's a list of film actors and actresses from Philippines, listed alphabetically with photos when available. The Philippines have produced some very talented actors and actresses, many of whom have gone on to star in comedies, dramas, horror movies, and many more. These Filipino actors specialize in film, television, or even theater, so they're not all necessarily movie stars, but they are all some of the best Filipino actors the country has ever seen, so if you're a Philippines native and an aspiring actor or actress, then you're likely to find many of your acting idols listed here.

The list includes Angel Lacy, J.C. Bonnin, and plenty more Filipino actors and Filipina actresses.

With this list, you can finally answer questions like, "Who are the best Filipino actors?" and "Which movie stars are from The Philippines?"

Click on the names of these famous movie stars of The Philippines in order to see more information about each one. If you're a film buff, use this list of talented Filipino film actors to find some new talents and movies you haven't already seen.
